item.title: Duke University - Duke Commencement Ceremony 2023
item.description: Video Transcript WELCOME TO DUKE UNIVERSITY’S 171ST COMMENCEMENT. PLEASE DIRECT YOUR ATTENTION TO THE END OF THE FIELD AND WELCOME THE DUKE UNIVERSITY CLASS OF 2023. NOW ENTERING THE STADIUM AND THROUGHOUT THE PROCESSIONAL MARCH ARE THE CANDIDATE’S DEGREES FROM ARTS AND SCIENCES WHO ARE JOINED THIS YEAR WHO ARE JOINED BY THE UNIVERSITY. ENTERING NOW ARE THE CANDIDATES FROM THE SCHOOL OF ENGINEERING. NEXT PLEASE WELCOME THE CANDIDATES FROM THE SANFORD SCHOOL OF PUBLIC POLICY.
